description.content:
Are you looking for a stunning, responsive, and fully custom website that meets your business goals?

I specialize in custom website design and development using WordPress redesigns to refresh and enhance existing sites.Whether you need a brand-new website to elevate your online presence, Ive got you covered.


What I Offer:

  • Custom Website Development
  • WordPress Redesign: Modern, user-friendly, and optimized layouts for existing WordPress sites or starting from scratch.
  • Responsive Design: A website that looks great on desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.
  • SEO Optimization
  • E-commerce Solutions: Integrated online stores with secure payment gateways, product listings, and more.
  • Speed Optimization


Why Choose Me?

  • Professional, Clean, and Eye-Catching layouts
  • Years of Experience in Web Development and WordPress
  • Fast Turnaround & Open Communication
  • 100% Client Satisfaction with Revisions as Needed


Process:

  1. Consultation: Understand your needs, preferences, and business goals.
  2. Design & Development: Create a customized, functional, and visually appealing site.
  3. Testing & Launch: Ensure the site is fully functional and responsive across all devices.|


Thank you!

reviews.comment:
This designer lacks attention to detail and does not take design requirements seriously.

There were many instances where I repeated the need for modifications 4 to 5 times, yet he failed to complete the changes until the delivery day. I had to submit a revision request, and only then did he make the adjustments. He later claimed it was not his fault, stating that the system's cache had not updated in time. However, the photos displayed on the webpage were disorganized, and he insisted that it was not his responsibility to fix these issues.

I requested a product list to be created, but at first, he simply listed a few products randomly on the same page. It was only after I asked him to redo it twice that he finally started creating a proper product list.

He displayed photos of varying sizes without any sense of aesthetics. Later, I asked him to upload photos of the same size from the ones I provided. Today, he claimed this was my fault. As a designer, he could have selected photos of the same size or asked me to provide ones that match. Instead, he uploaded them randomly, showing no attention to detail.

The language selection option was designed carelessly and was very unstable. I had to request modifications three times to address this.

Some of the titles and descriptions were completely unrelated to the photos. Although I could fix these issues myself, it shows how careless the designer was in his work.
